{"tid":984785,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"100名電工過年前追討數百萬欠薪 跑馬地地盤外示威","createTime":"2019-01-17T05:29:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-17T07:46:53.000Z","uid":41404,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c0efaeb1ab822f88955c20654f8e0d1ba6c24ea3","tid":984785,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T05:29:30.000Z","msg":"跑馬地桂芳街賽馬會會所地盤約100名工人疑遭拖欠薪金，中午集體到地盤門外示威。正午12時許，數十名地盤工人在地盤外示威追薪，他們舉起「有汗出，冇糧出」抗議標語示威。工人代表表示受影響工人主要為電工，人數約100名，遭二判僱主即建設工程有限公司及大判金門建築有限公司拖欠12月的基本工資及加班費，涉款估計逾600萬元。<br />\n<br />\n協助工友追薪的職工盟組織幹事何天忻稱，工友示威之前已多次接觸資方，但出糧時間卻被一拖再拖，「七日又七日」，由於年關將至，令工友十分憂心，雖然金門曾承諾下周一出票，但工人經已「冇晒信心」，要求即日出糧。職工盟在新聞稿則補充，若金門無合理回應，將不排除行動會升級。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190117/59152654\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190117%2F59152654&d=UvKuUuc4QvHjzgPyDvtmWwHZiNw4JStbf0cW9gpNrZc%3D&h=ff2a0c39\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190117%2F59152654&h=855ac0d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190117/59152654</a>"},{"pid":"00d86efdae15fe5f068aef416066b8197fc36117","tid":984785,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T05:31:02.000Z","msg":"賽馬會會所<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a74bdc956ff092e851afdac19792b17fdf08c05","tid":984785,"uid":58552,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T05:31:50.000Z","msg":"金門<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0536ff1a00faadb368b8c9b448cb6738b6d71d53","tid":984785,"uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T05:34:24.000Z","msg":"好似少聽開電燈佬追數"},{"pid":"857eedf579adae2bbd66979d0b6b4915feb5d65e","tid":984785,"uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"r